    "title" : "How to programmatically grant users permissions for actions with queues in Artemis?",
    "body" : "<p>I need to programmatically create users in Artemis and grant them access to some queues.</p>\n<p>I am currently using JMX for creating users. It works fine, but I cannot determine how to grant a specific user access to a specific queue (i.e. specify that user 'User1' can consume from or send to queue 'Queue1').</p>\n",
